Package: descriptiveStats
Type: Package
Title: Calculating descriptive statistics for numeric vectors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Polina", "Kornilova",
      email = "polina.kornilova2710@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: The package calculates statistics such as mean, median, mode, first quartile (25%),
    third quartile (75%), and interquantile range (IQR). It handles special cases such as empty vectors,
    NA values and single value vectors.
